Class SampledStatistic.SampleSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.uw.cs.cse461.util.SampledStatistic.SampleSet

    abstract static class SampledStatistic.SampleSet
extends Object
    A helper class. There is a SampleSet associated with each distinct timer key value. (Java makes it too clumsy to make this a generic, so we settle as double for the type of samples.)
